Class ErrorHandlerNull

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.imperio.ErrorHandlerNull
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ErrorHandler

    public class ErrorHandlerNull
extends java.lang.Object
implements ErrorHandler
    This ErrorHandler silently swallows all errors and warnings. However, firstError() will still return the first error type that occurs.
    Since:
    1.0.0
